{"tid":1059144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雪種爆炸 冷氣工不治","createTime":"2019-03-13T02:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T17:43:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"1c73065f51e5a6349c03dbc7d7ddd81826441a7e","tid":1059144,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:53:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190313/20632329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190313%2F20632329&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BfG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=75f3a784\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190313%2F20632329&h=0f50c3fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190313/20632329</a><br />\n<br />\n雪種爆炸 冷氣工不治<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190313/large/13la4p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190313%2Flarge%2F13la4p6.jpg&h=3e0de9fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n技工從四米高墮地重創，送院搶救終告不治。司徒韋桐攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名冷氣技工前晚在荃灣德士古道DHL服務中心攀上長梯維修分體冷氣機期間，懷疑冷氣機雪種突然爆炸，巨大衝擊力將技工炸飛，從四米高長梯上墮地重創，送院搶救至昨午不治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n40人疏散<br />\n<br />\n29歲死者陳卓人，未婚，與家人居於沙田瀝源邨，為DHL一間外判承辦商的冷氣技工。現場為德士古道100號DHL服務中心倉庫，前晚8時許，陳與工友到上址維修冷氣機，他攀鋁梯上四米高閣樓維修分體式冷氣機，其間，懷疑壓縮雪種樽突然發生爆炸，陳被強大爆炸氣流擊中後，從鋁梯跌落地面，面、頸及胸部重傷昏迷，18歲姓林同事見狀報警。警員及救護員到場，先將他送往仁濟醫院搶救，其後轉送瑪嘉烈醫院，消防員到場戒備，大廈約40人疏散。陳送院後情況一直危殆，並因傷重延至昨午3時半終告不治。警方調查後，列作工業意外有人死亡案件跟進。<br />\nDHL Express對事故表示難過，向承辦商員工家屬致以哀悼。<br />\n<br />\n■記者司徒韋桐、姜偉康  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n醫生工會晤林鄭 促改革醫管局<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n阿牛申覆核狙擊梁振英 要求頒令律政司就UGL案提控"},{"pid":"9ed5ad8f1c17a70cd831d7cb6829b5bf6db1ea86","tid":1059144,"uid":113626,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:54:29.000Z","msg":"等睇老貓審判佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf541ff07b4bf19a410328ba7b2e13a2854ee9d","tid":1059144,"uid":57677,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:55:22.000Z","msg":"其實雪種有冇毒性？"},{"pid":"a5aee5c0e2a38ec7992786b9d6af12e7bab7c2fd","tid":1059144,"uid":57677,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:59:41.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】一名29歲男工人前晚到荃灣DHL快遞的倉庫維修冷氣，<span style=\"color: red;\">其間冷凝器突然爆炸</span>，他從4米高木梯墮地，面、頸及胸部被炸傷，昏迷送院，延至昨午不治。"},{"pid":"0a7ebac39e760c1dc2115996eebd289f321dcad9","tid":1059144,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"a5aee5c0e2a38ec7992786b9d6af12e7bab7c2fd","tid":1059144,"uid":57677,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:59:41.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】一名29歲男工人前晚到荃灣DHL快遞的倉庫維修冷氣，<span style=\"color: red;\">其間冷凝器突然爆炸</span>，他從4米高木梯墮地，面、頸及胸部被炸傷，昏迷送院，延至昨午不治。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T03:05:44.000Z","msg":"究竟係雪種樽定係冷凝器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28251c668dc5bc4117aa28f94da7460b62b6d592","tid":1059144,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bf541ff07b4bf19a410328ba7b2e13a2854ee9d","tid":1059144,"uid":57677,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:55:22.000Z","msg":"其實雪種有冇毒性？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T03:06:18.000Z","msg":"冇 不過好似聞得多都唔好 咩肝硬化定點"},{"pid":"881c54c7e379d0e5170c1639a4aef397ff65d180","tid":1059144,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T03:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856400a0ad3af5c848ab54d45db7d65723ee0c01","tid":1059144,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T03:13:04.000Z","msg":"返工 = <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115ec71e292a785f3c9c8efcad8c8d7cea523b69","tid":1059144,"uid":10